00:00:40.495 --> 00:00:46.858
INTRODUCTION TO
IFRAME EMBEDDED PLAYER

00:00:48.297 --> 00:00:50.594
There are different options

00:00:50.594 --> 00:00:52.429
for the Embedded Player.

00:00:52.429 --> 00:00:56.198
There's the Flash AS3, AS2
Embedded Player

00:00:56.198 --> 00:00:59.660
and also the Embedded
Player in an iFrame.

00:00:59.660 --> 00:01:02.825
The iFrame is the most
recommended option

00:01:02.825 --> 00:01:05.924
because this way
YouTube can decide

00:01:05.924 --> 00:01:08.066
which Player will be downloaded

00:01:08.066 --> 00:01:11.033
in the iFrame to play videos.

00:01:11.033 --> 00:01:14.231
It's worth remembering
that there are devices

00:01:14.231 --> 00:01:17.957
that can not support Flash,
such as iPad and iPhone.

00:01:17.957 --> 00:01:21.495
There are two ways to create
an iFrame Embedded Player,

00:01:21.495 --> 00:01:23.759
one is through JavaScript,

00:01:23.759 --> 00:01:26.198
and the other by directly
declaring the iFrame.

00:01:26.198 --> 00:01:29.363
In this lesson,
to make it easier,

00:01:29.363 --> 00:01:32.924
we will directly declare
an iFrame to use URL parameters

00:01:32.924 --> 00:01:36.495
that modify its appearance
and behavior.

00:01:36.495 --> 00:01:39.099
The simplest way
for obtaining code

00:01:39.099 --> 00:01:41.792
to embed the iFrame Player

00:01:41.792 --> 00:01:45.066
is by using the code
shown in the Share option

00:01:45.066 --> 00:01:47.495
when we watch a YouTube video.

00:01:47.495 --> 00:01:49.990
The Embedded Player

00:01:49.990 --> 00:01:51.726
has a series,
of standard controls.

00:01:51.726 --> 00:01:54.165
such as the Play Button,
Pause Button,

00:01:54.165 --> 00:01:57.990
Volume Control,
Progress BarÉ

00:01:57.990 --> 00:02:01.396
We can personalize these
through parameters

00:02:01.396 --> 00:02:03.825
as well as Player behavior.

00:02:03.825 --> 00:02:06.693
We do this through
URL parameters.

00:02:06.693 --> 00:02:10.165
We also specify through the URL
the video we want to watch.

00:02:10.165 --> 00:02:13.561
We can use, for example,
the Autoplay parameter,

00:02:13.561 --> 00:02:16.924
and this way the video
will begin automatically

00:02:16.924 --> 00:02:18.891
with no user intervention.

00:02:18.891 --> 00:02:22.792
Other than for personalizing
the Player by parameters,

00:02:22.792 --> 00:02:25.792
the API allows us
to monitor its activities

00:02:25.792 --> 00:02:28.825
and control it
through JavaScript.

00:02:28.825 --> 00:02:31.561
But we'll see this
in the next lesson.

